item.title: Different risk of getting Covid-19 at different Age level
item.description: Introduction At the beginning of the 2020, the outbreak of global pandemic (Covid-19) causes the global panic in public health, economy, society and so on. More and more people is being impacted by this global pandemic, and it is important for us to know how to protect people from the illness for specific age group. This provides us motivation for studing which age group has the most risk of being sick.
